\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd27bc5fd53c7490cd90b9276a110db4d7924ab4","tid":1660441,"uid":163024,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T20:33:51.000Z","msg":"唔知你讀文科定理科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我讀理科一開始就係上晒啲堂，鳩坐喺度聽到1999<br />\n返學發夢雙主線真係好撚辛苦，後尾發現咁唔係辦法就開始搵出路<br />\n我今個禮拜開始走晒啲堂喺屋企自學，點知效率仲高過我日日準時返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日訓到自然醒，鍾意幾時讀書就幾時讀書，攰咗就訓陣起身繼續讀<br />\n果日如果有行動就skip一日之後繼續<br />\n<br />\n大學嘅真諦就係只要交足assignment，test唔好唔見人，其實走足成個sem都唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n社交方面我都無埋堆，不過本身有上大莊所以可能好啲"},{"pid":"99bbe75c2abf5ef7f78a5fa6ee1de04ed0acd92a","tid":1660441,"uid":22577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58de4bbe25214979d9255f36d5bd9d9401150cf1","tid":1660441,"uid":321650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e42e5eaa298a8b6da076b6de6328a4398b1d1a8","tid":1660441,"uid":22577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"同你諗一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不如tg講？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:27:57.000Z","msg":"[member]<a href=\"https://t.me/hihiihiii[/member］\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhihiihiii%5B%2Fmember%EF%BC%BD&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAYdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=00379ebd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hihiihiii[/member］</a>"},{"pid":"2d9901af67dc00f88aea65edc97e6c16585db4a6","tid":1660441,"uid":210944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8bc50797667350db540db96f743b67f263d0a565","tid":1660441,"uid":321650,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"abefcc444827bbfc3afc5056e8e9797bba449244","tid":1660441,"uid":137665,"like":9,"dislike":0,